HEADWORD: Self-fertilization
<hw>Self`-fer`ti*li*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The fertilization of a flower by pollen from the
same flower and without outer aid; autogamy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-fertilized</ent>⟦br⟧
